{"title":"Zwift Returns to Jarvis Island Celebrating 10 Years of Indoor Cycling","link":"https://bikerumor.com/zwift-returns-to-jarvis-island-celebrating-10-years-of-indoor-cycling/","date":1731432406000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-brigde--1536x864.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route brigde\" /></p>\n<p><em>Zwift is turning back the clock while looking to the future with the return of Jarvis Island, the platform’s original virtual cycling world.</em> Initially launched over a decade ago, Jarvis Island gave a new dimension to indoor training. As part of Zwift’s 10-year celebrations, the island has re-emerged, blending nostalgia with modern enhancements.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--jpg.webp\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--jpg.webp 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>2025: Return to Jarvis Island </h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Nestled off the coast of Watopia’s famous Volcano Mountain, Jarvis Island 2025 is more than just a nod to the past—it’s a full-on upgrade. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--jpg.webp\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route tree through\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--jpg.webp 1920w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-tree-through--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Expect to spot revamped landmarks,  goofy references to the early days <em>(blue bots, anyone?)</em>, and even a Banjo Man Café. For those new to Zwift, this expansion offers a chance to ride a piece of history. For the OG beta testers, it’s a homecoming.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route in the city\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--1200x675.webp 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-in-the-city--jpg.webp 1920w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route fences\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--1200x675.webp 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-fences--jpg.webp 1920w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--jpg.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Zwift Return to Jarvis route mountains\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--1200x675.webp 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Zwift-Return-to-Jarvis-route-mountains--jpg.webp 1920w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Six New Routes – Endless Riding Options</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><span><strong>Deca Dash</strong>: </span>Ten laps spanning 52.4 km of climbs and sharp turns. Pushing riders to their limit on every pedal stroke.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span><strong>Wasted 8</strong>:</span> An eight-lap, 30.7 km route traversing deserts and ocean views, ideal for those craving flat yet scenic rides.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span><strong>Loopin’ Lava</strong>:</span> A fiery 18.3 km ride around Watopia’s volcanic landscape. Designed to keep the heat on for riders seeking a demanding climbing challenge.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span><strong>The Classic</strong>:</span> Experience the timeless beauty of Watopia. This 8.8 km route combines elements of old and new. Showcasing Zwift’s origins and some of the most scenic roads on the island.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span><strong>Coast to Coast</strong>:</span> A diverse 24.1 km journey starting at the southern shore and featuring the Sasquatch Sprint. Woodland Sprint, Jarvis KOM, and Jarvis Sprint to challenge Zwifters on every stretch.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong><span>Triple Twist:</span></strong> Ideal for riders looking to test their speed over 24.4 km with three tight loops incorporating the Zwift and Jarvis KOMs and Jarvis Sprint and Lap segments for pace improvements.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Each Zwifter will experience the dramatic reveal of Jarvis Island upon their first visit, complete with sights, sounds, and a touch of surprise. To learn more about the comeback of Jarvis Island and the expansion of Watopia, check out<a href=\"http://zwift.com/watopia-expansion\"> zwift.com/watopia-expansion</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/zwift-returns-to-jarvis-island-celebrating-10-years-of-indoor-cycling/\">Zwift Returns to Jarvis Island Celebrating 10 Years of Indoor Cycling</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"232b1d055d7dfa2822df724dcc3a1f20dc37c3ccc16ef38f02cdeda56288bad6","category":"Cycling"}